entry.def: Someone who is brimful of an emotion or quality feels or seems full of it. An object or place that is brimful of something is full of it.

example.ex: She was brimful of energy and enthusiasm...
The United States is brimful with highly paid doctors.
example.tran: 美国有很多薪酬很高的医生。
